originalText.text:
My roommate and I had the absolute pleasure of working with Josh over the past couple of months. From our initial meeting to the final closing, Josh was helpful, professional, and knowledgeable every step of the way. He really took the time to understand our needs and preferences and provided valuable guidance throughout what can be a confusing and frustrating process. Josh was very communicative and patient with us - we never felt like he was trying to push us towards an apartment that we didn't absolutely love.

I would recommend Josh to anyone looking for a new place in NYC. Thank you, Josh!

originalText.text:
I cannot recommend Josh highly enough! Working with him has been an absolute pleasure from start to finish. Not only was he consistently punctual, but his commitment to providing exceptional service was evident in every interaction we had.

First and foremost, Josh's punctuality was impressive. Throughout our entire business relationship, he was always on time, whether it was for meetings, phone calls, or sending important documents. This level of professionalism made the entire process smooth and efficient, as I never had to worry about delays or missed opportunities.

One of the standout qualities of Josh is his ability to deliver outstanding consultations. He took the time to understand my goals and concerns. With his extensive knowledge and expertise, he provided valuable insights and personalized advice that proved to be instrumental in making informed decisions in the NYC apartment search. Josh's recommendations were always clear, well-researched, and tailored to my specific preferences.

Efficiency is another area where Josh truly shines. He wasted no time in handling paperwork, negotiations, and any other tasks related to our transactions. Thanks to his proactive approach, I felt confident that everything was being handled swiftly and accurately.

Overall, my experience with Josh has been nothing short of exceptional. He has set the bar high for what a broker should be and I will be using him again in the future!
